---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Ultimate Summer Chalets, part of Blue Skies Lifestyle Ltd."
>
  <div class="bg-navy-dark py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-gold text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 prose prose-gray">

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: March 2018. This policy applies to Ultimate Summer Chalets, operated by Blue Skies Lifestyle Limited (Company No. 05493155, England and Wales), 170 Charminster Road, Bournemouth, Dorset, BH8 9RL.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect From You</h2>
    <p><strong>1.1 Personal information you provide to us may include:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full names, dates of birth, passport information</li>
      <li>Full addresses and nationality</li>
      <li>Email addresses and telephone numbers</li>
      <li>Dietary requirements, special requests, and personal preferences</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>1.2 Technical information collected automatically:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>IP addresses, browser type and version, time zone settings</li>
      <li>Pages visited, clickstream data, page response times</li>
      <li>Page interaction information (scrolling, clicks, mouse-overs)</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>1.3</strong> We also work with third parties (business partners, analytics providers, search information providers) who may provide us with information about you.</p>

    <p><strong>1.4</strong> We may retain preference and demographic information inferred from your interactions with our website.</p>

    <p><strong>1.5</strong> We collect information on email responses including open rates and link clicks.</p>

    <p><strong>1.6</strong> Information you submit may be retained for at least twelve (12) months after collection or as reasonably necessary.</p>

    <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
    <p>A cookie is a simple text file stored on your computer or mobile device by a website's server. Cookies help us distinguish users from one another, improve your browsing experience, and allow us to improve our site.</p>

    <p><strong>We use the following types of cookie:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> — to understand which pages are being used and how visitors navigate the site. You can opt out at <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-gold hover:underline">tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Session cookies</strong> — temporary cookies that exist only while you access our site, helping pages remember your previous selections.</li>
      <li><strong>Third-party marketing cookies</strong> — used within social media and email campaigns to track activity initiated from marketing links.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>You can manage or disable cookies through your browser. Visit <a href="http://www.allaboutcookies.org/manage-cookies/" class="text-gold hover:underline">allaboutcookies.org</a> for guidance. To block only non-essential cookies, allow the cookie CAKEPHP.</p>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p><strong>We use the information we hold about you to:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide you with the information, products, and services you request</li>
      <li>Pass relevant details to suppliers of your holiday arrangements (chalet owners, transport companies, etc.) as necessary for your booking</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations, including requests from customs, immigration, and financial checking authorities</li>
      <li>Inform you about similar products and services we offer</li>
      <li>Notify you about changes to our service</li>
      <li>Administer our website and carry out internal analysis, testing, and research</li>
      <li>Keep our website safe and secure</li>
      <li>Measure advertising effectiveness and deliver relevant advertising to you</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Disclosure of Your Information</h2>
    <p>We may share your personal information with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Any member of our group (subsidiaries, holding company, and its subsidiaries)</li>
      <li>Business partners, suppliers, and sub-contractors for the performance of any contract</li>
      <li>Analytics and search engine providers who assist in website improvement</li>
      <li>A prospective buyer in the event of a sale of our business or assets</li>
      <li>Authorities where required by law, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of our company, customers, or others</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Where We Store Your Personal Data</h2>
    <p>The data we collect is stored on our servers based in the UK. For international bookings, data may be transferred outside the European Economic Area (EEA) and processed by staff outside the EEA working for suppliers. By submitting your personal data, you agree to this transfer, storage, and processing.</p>
    <p>We take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure your data is treated securely. Unfortunately, internet transmission is not completely secure; any transmission is at your own risk. Once received, we use strict procedures and security features to prevent unauthorised access.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We are registered with the ICO under the Data Protection Act and adhere to the following principles:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access to your information is restricted to relevant trained staff only</li>
      <li>Hard copies of confidential documents are kept securely under lock and key</li>
      <li>All relevant employees receive training on handling information safely</li>
      <li>We periodically evaluate our database and securely delete information no longer needed</li>
      <li>All personal information is stored in secure web-hosted environments accessible only by key personnel</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our Data Processor and Data Controller can be contacted at <a href="mailto:ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to ask us not to process your personal data for marketing purposes and to exercise your right to be forgotten. You can do so by:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Telephone: <a href="tel:+441202203659" class="text-gold hover:underline">+44 (0)1202 203659</a></li>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com</a> (put "unsubscribe" in the subject line)</li>
      <li>Post: 170 Charminster Road, Bournemouth, Dorset, BH8 9RL</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our website may contain links to third-party sites. Those sites have their own privacy policies, and we accept no responsibility for them. Please check their policies before submitting personal data.</p>

    <h2>8. Access to Your Information</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access the personal information we hold about you. Requests can be made by telephone, email, or post using the contact details above. We will endeavour to supply that information within thirty (30) days of receipt of your request.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Any changes we make to our Privacy Policy will be posted on this page and, where appropriate, notified to you by email. Please check back periodically to see any updates.</p>

    <h2>10. Jurisdiction</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy is governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England. The parties irrevocably agree that the English Courts shall have exclusive jurisdiction to settle any dispute arising out of or in connection with this policy.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions, comments, and requests regarding this Privacy Policy are welcome. Please contact us at:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Telephone: <a href="tel:+441202203659" class="text-gold hover:underline">+44 (0)1202 203659</a></li>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">ask@ultimatesummerchalets.com</a></li>
      <li>Post: 170 Charminster Road, Bournemouth, Dorset, BH8 9RL</li>
    </ul>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    @apply font-serif text-2xl text-navy mt-10 mb-4;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-1 text-gray-700;
  }
  .prose li {
    @apply leading-relaxed;
  }
</style>
